description: There are fears France's fastest growing city this decade could be vulnerable after the pandemic.
title: Coronavirus: France's boom city Toulouse shaken by pandemic
title_page: Coronavirus: France's boom city Toulouse shaken by pandemic - BBC News
maintext: Until Covid-19 struck, most of the sector was booming. Now it's reeling as airlines have no idea when they can resume flights or when they will require new planes. France's fourth city has seen relatively few cases of coronavirus and yet suddenly it is looking vulnerable to the fallout of the pandemic.
